      "comment": "GO WILD GYPSY (7) was speedy out of box 6 on debut to score by 1.75 lengths (16.84) at Q Straight over 300m. Drawn wide but has good early pace. Should be in this for a long way. SPRING HALLIE (8) proved too good on debut over 350m at Goulburn to score by 2.25 lengths (20.17). Drawn wide but has good early pace. Harder here but expected to measure up. MISS SPRITZ (4) showed good pace from out wide and was prominent throughout before fading out of it when 8th at this track in a Grade 6. The form out of last run is most impressive. Should be in this for a long way. BONES (1) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.",
